    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older vehicle in poor overall condition and priced accordingly. It runs and drives, but it shows significant wear from age and use, with noticeable cosmetic flaws inside and out, tired-looking finishes, and the kind of deferred maintenance and upkeep an older vehicle often needs. This is not a clean or like-new example, but for someone looking for basic transportation, a budget option, or a project, it may be worth a look. Buyers should expect an honest, well-used vehicle that will likely need attention to bring up to a higher standard.",
